title: Changing The Story You Tell Yourself
description:
Consciously or subconsciously, we all tell ourselves stories that color our worldview. But do you know what yours is? Is it true? And even more, is it serving you? Chelsea and Judah break down how to identify what story you’ve been telling yourself and, if necessary, how to change it — so you can be the best you, for yourself and others.
